_sText:
This map took me about 30 mins to make and about 10 secs to build with lighting, its a small combat, deathmatch map if you would say xD i got bored so i made it from the top of my head so dont flame to me please ^^
Also the water in the middle, if you go to far under there is a trigger_hurt which will kill you straight away.
Installation>>>> Place the maps into your cstrike map folder.
